{"type": "article", "id": 6177, "title": "吃海鲜专用餐具 Colombina 系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-13T07:40:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234137Pq0SXYB4h1pIGg6k.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自意大利的设计师 Doriana 与 Massimiliano Fuksas 今年携手为意大利餐具品牌 Alessi 带来了一套吃海鲜时专用的餐具 Colombina 系列，包括了鱼肉叉、刀、匙三件套，分菜叉、刀、匙三件套；以及牡蛎叉，黄油刀，鱼子酱匙，贝壳钳和贝类叉等 11 件为满足海鲜类菜品准备、服务和用餐等各个阶段需要而设计的餐具。两位设计师为每件餐具都富裕了鱼鳞纹一般的图案，在设计过程中充分考虑到了人们在食用海鲜时的各种需求，如怎样讲贝壳中的肉取出的方式更加便捷，怎样才是涂抹黄油与鱼子酱的最佳工具等等。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234134XIzgbjfuDLqNioac.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234135XEGPRlU9Igsv4Dfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234135Ea4ODWzidm1VPIUf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234135jSQOUwyT0koemaf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.271875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234136C1JA7lzPcL9nEmfu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341365OPYVDw2RK4acl1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}